nodes.text: Level 45 was a district in the Sliver, a settlement on the planet Kaddak. It was home to a cantina that was frequented by various groups including Kanjiklub and the Guavian Death Gang. In 34 ABY, the Resistance operatives Poe Dameron, C-3PO, BB-8, and Oddy Muva visited Level 45 during a mission to recover a Resistance spy droid who supposedly had valuable information about the First Order.
